<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="certainly-adv">certainly <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'sɜːtnli/    美 /'sɜːrtnli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>必然；肯定地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Something was certainly wrong with him. 
他肯定出问题了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>If I had time, I would certainly go for outing with you. 
如果有时间，我肯定会跟你去远足。</p><footer>2012 湖南</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>当然；没问题：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Will you help me?
你愿意帮我的忙吗？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Certainly I will.
当然愿意。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Do you mind if I sit here?
我坐这儿你介意吗？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— <strong>Certainly not</strong>. 
当然不会。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>— May I ask a question after class, Sir?
— <strong><em>_</em></strong>_(certain), but not during my lunch break.  （2008 重庆改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. Certainly  </p></div>